'''Rashi Bawa''' yɛ Ghanani amanyoni, ɔman ananmusini ne amanyɔkuo New Partriotic Party no mu ni. Ɔyɛ Ghana ananmusini a ɔwɔ Nigeria. Ɔyɛ Kane Ghana ananmusin a ɔwɔ Saudi Arabia. Ɔyɛ kane mmarahyɛ baguani.

== Ɔman ananmusifo ==
IWƆ July afe 2017 mu no, ɔmanpanyin Nana Akuffo-Addo paw Rashi Bawa sɛ [[Ghana]] ananmusifo wɔ Nigeria. Na ɔka nnipa a wɔn dodoɔ yɛ aduonu mienu a wɔpaw wɔn sɛ wonkɔ som sɛ Ghana ananmusifo wɔ aman ahorɔw so.

